WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.500
Meanwhile, in the web development department,
things were equally chaotic.

2
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:08.200
DEVELOPER: The client wants captions
on their HTML5 video player.

3
00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:12.000
DEVELOPER: They sent us SRT files.
HTML5 only supports WebVTT.

4
00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:16.200
MANAGER: Can't you just rename
the file extension?

5
00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:20.500
DEVELOPER: That's not how
file formats work, Karen.

6
00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:24.500
MANAGER: My name isn't Karen.

7
00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:28.200
DEVELOPER: I know. I'm sorry.
The deadline stress is getting to me.

8
00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:32.500
DEVELOPER: Wait - ConvertICO has an
SRT to VTT converter. Problem solved!

9
00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:36.500
MANAGER: See? That wasn't so hard.

10
00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:40.000
DEVELOPER: [silently screams
into coffee mug]
